{"tid":1625672,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"搞美心之前知唔知佢母公司係咩？","createTime":"2019-10-05T07:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T08:01:09.000Z","uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9c803a2ce4ebd7471b12d7b023bcbb7da1634179","tid":1625672,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:51:21.000Z","msg":"以下內容轉自維基百科<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-yue.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/牛奶公司\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E7%89%9B%E5%A5%B6%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KE2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=9666d870\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh-yue.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/牛奶公司</a><br />\n<br />\n牛奶公司（英文Dairy Farm）係亞洲搞零沽業務嘅公司，1886年喺香港開張，一路都係賣牛奶產品，1973年畀怡和洋行旗下嘅置地公司收購，開始將業務逐漸轉到零沽嗰邊。而家佢喺香港經營嘅業務包括<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7-11便利店</span></span>、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">惠康超級市場</span></span>、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">萬寧藥房</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">、宜家家居</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">美心食品</span></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">之前怡和出賣左大家，唔係放過惠康同萬寧下嘛？</span></span>"},{"pid":"2ab76f0da0d9b3186f18864c8c0c572eaeb1cd4c","tid":1625672,"uid":281822,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:01:09.000Z","msg":"美心係因為佢另一半股東，姓伍條撚樣先抵死<br />\n怡和係另一半股東，死3毛又亂帶方向<br />\n<br />\n落地獄啦"}]}